  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[On Play] Reveal the top 3 cards of your deck. Add 1 Digimon
    card with [X Antibody] in its traits and 1 Option card with [X Antibody] in its
    traits among them to your hand. Place the rest at the bottom of your deck in
    any order. [Your Turn] When one of your Digimon digivolves into a same-level
    Digimon with [X Antibody] in its traits, you may suspend this Tamer to gain 1
    memory and \uFF1CDraw 1\uFF1E."
